  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a new non-contact biometer, is as accurate
      as the the available gold-standard.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The features of a not yet commercial available new biometer will be compared to available
      contact and non contact biometers in different patient groups.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
